## FontSize Naming Rules

### Use meaningful names
```dart
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Clear names
static const double fontSizeSmall = 12.0;
static const double fontSizeBody = 14.0;
static const double fontSizeTitle = 18.0;
static const double fontSizeHeading = 24.0;

// Usage
TextStyle(fontSize: fontSizeSmall.sp)
TextStyle(fontSize: fontSizeBody.sp)
```

### Or use enum
```dart
enum AppFontSize {
  small(12.0),
  body(14.0),
  title(18.0),
  heading(24.0);
  
  const AppFontSize(this.size);
  final double size;
  
  double get sp => size.sp;
}

// Usage
TextStyle(fontSize: AppFontSize.title.sp)
```

