## Best Practices

### 1. Use constants
```dart
class AppFontSizes {
  static const double xs = 10.0;
  static const double sm = 12.0;
  static const double md = 14.0;
  static const double lg = 16.0;
  static const double xl = 18.0;
  static const double xxl = 20.0;
  static const double xxxl = 24.0;
}

// Usage
TextStyle(fontSize: AppFontSizes.lg.sp)
```

### 2. Use extension
```dart
extension FontSizeExtension on double {
  double get sp => this.sp;
}

// Usage
TextStyle(fontSize: 16.sp)
```

### 3. Use mixin
```dart
mixin FontSizeMixin {
  double get fontSizeSmall => 12.sp;
  double get fontSizeBody => 14.sp;
  double get fontSizeTitle => 18.sp;
  double get fontSizeHeading => 24.sp;
}

class MyWidget extends StatelessWidget with FontSizeMixin {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Text(
      'Hello',
      style: TextStyle(fontSize: fontSizeTitle),
    );
  }
}
```

## Checking and Validation

### Pre-commit Hook
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Check fontSize in code
grep -r "fontSize: [0-9]" lib/ | grep -v ".sp"
if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
  echo "‚ùå Found fontSize not using .sp"
  exit 1
fi
echo "‚úÖ All fontSize uses .sp"
```

